This is awesome!!! Very delicious. I will definatelty make it again. Read the other reviews and made the following modifications: cut sugar back to 1/2 cup. Perfect sweetness for me. You can always gradually add more after adding the cream if you want it sweeter. Added 1/4 of rum as with the cinnamon, the 2 tbsp of rum could not be tasted. This was the perfect combo for me.

